350  PRINT "    TELESCOPE'S OBJECTIVE"
360  PRINT 
370  PRINT " 2) FILM IN CAMERA AND CAMERA"
380  PRINT "    AT EYEPIECE OF TELESCOPE"
390  PRINT "    WITH CAMERA LENS IN USE"
400  PRINT 
